quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  25,45,Ese ntubona uko Nyagasani wawe arambura igicucu? N’iyo aza kubishaka yari kukigumisha hamwe. Hanyuma izuba twarigize ikimenyetso cyacyo
  25,46,Maze tukagenda tukigabanya tukigarura iwacu buhoro buhoro
  25,47,"Kandi ni We (Allah) wabagiriye ijoro kuba nk’umwambaro (ubahishira), ibitotsi abigira ikiruhuko ndetse n’amanywa ayagira igihe cyo gushakisha imibereho"
  25,48,"Ni na We wohereza imiyaga itanga icyizere, ibanziriza impuhwe ze (imvura); kandi tumanura mu kirere amazi asukuye"
  25,49,"Kugira ngo dusubize ubuzima ubutaka bwapfuye (bwakakaye), kandi tunayanywesha byinshi mu byo twaremye; (yaba) amatungo ndetse n’abantu"
  25,50,"Kandi rwose (imvura) twarayibasaranganyije kugira ngo batekereze (inema za Allah), ariko abenshi mu bantu baranze bahitamo guhakana"
  25,51,N’iyo dushaka twari kohereza umuburizi muri buri mudugudu
  25,52,"Bityo ntuzumvire abahakanyi, ahubwo ujye uhangana na bo (ubigisha) uyifashishije (Qur’an)"
  25,53,"Kandi (Allah) ni We wahuje inyanja ebyiri; ifite amazi y’urubogobogo amara inyota, naho indi ikaba urwunyunyu rukaze. Maze ashyira urubibi hagati yazo rutuma zitivanga"
  25,54,"Ndetse ni na We waremye umuntu amukomoye mu mazi (intanga), anamushyiriraho uburyo azajya agira amasano binyuze mu maraso ndetse no gushyingiranwa. Kandi Nyagasani wawe ni Ushobora byose"
  25,55,(Abahakanyi) basenga ibitari Allah bitagira icyo bibamarira cyangwa ngo bigire icyo bibatwara. Kandi umuhakanyi afatanya (na Shitani) kwigomeka kuri Nyagasani we
  25,56,Kandi nta kindi twakoherereje usibye kuba utanga inkuru nziza (yo kuzagororerwa ijuru ku bazumvira Allah) ndetse n’umuburizi (ku bazigomeka)
  25,57,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ntabwo (kubagezaho ubutumwa) mbibasabira igihembo, ariko uzashaka gukurikira inzira imuganisha kwa Nyagasani we (yemerewe kugira icyo atanga mu nzira ya Allah ku bushake bwe).”"
  25,58,"Ujye uniringira Uhoraho (Nyirubuzima bwuzuye), Udapfa, unamusingize umushima. Kandi arahagije kuba azi byimazeyo ibyaha by’abagaragu be"
  25,59,"We waremye ibirere n’isi ndetse n’ibiri hagati yabyo mu minsi itandatu, hanyuma Nyirimpuhwe (Allah) aganza hejuru ya Ar’shi. Bityo (yewe Muhamadi) mubaze ibijyanye na We (akwibwire kuko) ariyizi neza"
  25,60,N’iyo (abahakanyi) babwiwe bati “Nimwubamire Nyirimpuhwe!” Baravuga bati “Nyirimpuhwe nde? Ese tugomba kubamira uwo (wowe Muhamadi) udutegetse?” Nuko ibyo bikabongerera guhunga (ukuri)